spec_data.Name: php-ZendFramework-Services
spec_data.Description:
This package contains web service client APIs for the following services:

- Akismet
- Amazon (including EC2, S3)
- Audioscrobbler
- del.icio.us
- eBay
- Flickr
- LiveDocx
- Nirvanix
- Rackspace
- ReCaptcha
- Various URL Shortener services
- SlideShare
- SqlAzure
- StrikeIron
- Twitter
- Windows Azure
- Yahoo!
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 07:20:50 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Web service APIs for a number of providers
